Dependencies:

  gcc 4.4+ or clang 3.0+
  libevent 1.4+
  glibc or libevent 2.0+        (for DNS resolution)
  python 3.1+                   (for generating bytecode)
  gdb                           (for printing backtraces)

Build instructions:

  ./bootstrap.sh
  ./autogen.sh
  ./configure
  make all

Mac OS X prerequisites:

  - Install gcc46 from macports (http://www.macports.org)
  - Create config.mk at the top-level directory containing lines:
      CC  = gcc-mp-4.6
      CXX = g++-mp-4.6

